{"tid":2445162,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到完場］第16屆KKBOX音樂風雲榜","createTime":"2021-03-13T11:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T14:26:51.000Z","uid":48124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f481edd59523323af3e89c20a0a2dc61bd3abfba","tid":2445162,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gft3577UpNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGft3577UpNY&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=e067c283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gft3577UpNY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樂壇年度音樂盛事《第16屆KKBOX音樂風雲榜》將於明天（13日）晚上7時喺臺北流行音樂中心舉行。今年大會以「 Turn Up 放大聲音」為主題，將成個風雲榜「放大」，除咗聽晚嘅頒獎典禮之外，更擴大舉辦成連續兩天（13日及14日）「催下去音樂節」。<br />\n<br />\n早前KKBOX宣布頒獎典禮由Lulu（黃路梓茵）擔任主持人及出席歌手嘅名單，今年名單陣容多元化，包括八三夭、五堅情、田馥甄、瘦子、閻奕格、Julia 吳卓源、魏如萱、茄子蛋、李友廷、Kimberley 陳芳語、告五人、沒有才能、李芷婷 Nasi、李浩瑋 Howard Lee、采子、Asiaboy 禁藥王 &amp; Lizi 栗子、?te 壞特、G22、HowZ、Jinbo、8lak。歌手們將輪流上陣表演，打造最精彩舞台，大家千祈唔好錯過喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQTNKre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQTNKre.png&h=97c41281&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53bad1aa6859c82e7cd1126e6f207a2145830c72","tid":2445162,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216ca57019d788d4750649f7f8ff32e083607b4d","tid":2445162,"uid":48124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53bad1aa6859c82e7cd1126e6f207a2145830c72","tid":2445162,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:52:49.000Z","msg":"係唔係想去邊就去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf7ce668ed5b11d677460612156660e4998d778","tid":2445162,"uid":41998,"like":1,"dislike"